Let go of my daughter.

442
00:36:12,640 --> 00:36:14,920
<i>If I didn’t have my period,</i>

443
00:36:15,000 --> 00:36:19,080
would I have to carry feces
and urine like the laborer ladies?

444
00:36:25,280 --> 00:36:26,400
Talom.

445
00:36:26,480 --> 00:36:27,400
Mother.

446
00:36:30,320 --> 00:36:31,160
Where's the cloth?

447
00:36:34,800 --> 00:36:37,160
Keep this. Don't let anyone see it.

448
00:36:37,760 --> 00:36:41,600
Return to the training house.
I'll bring more blood next month.

449
00:36:42,200 --> 00:36:43,040
Alright.

450
00:37:04,560 --> 00:37:08,640
That's the girl I said
always got scolded as I did.

451
00:37:12,000 --> 00:37:13,800
I searched Talom's bed

452
00:37:14,640 --> 00:37:16,800
and found the blood-soaked cloth
and this bottle.

453
00:37:27,760 --> 00:37:30,000
It is certainly bird’s blood.

454
00:37:44,480 --> 00:37:46,160
What shall I do

455
00:37:46,960 --> 00:37:48,760
with these two sinners?

456
00:37:51,560 --> 00:37:55,360
You lied about having your period.

457
00:37:56,280 --> 00:37:57,680
And you,

458
00:37:58,560 --> 00:38:00,760
you have taken the lives of the birds.

459
00:38:01,480 --> 00:38:03,800
Your behavior is unsuitable

460
00:38:03,880 --> 00:38:06,880
for living in this paradise.

461
00:38:08,080 --> 00:38:11,720
- Cut their tongues.
- Cut their tongues.

462
00:38:11,800 --> 00:38:14,880
- Cut their tongues.
