463
00:38:14,960 --> 00:38:19,640
- Cut their tongues.
- Cut their tongues.

464
00:38:20,720 --> 00:38:22,800
Get away.

465
00:38:24,760 --> 00:38:26,240
Kick us out.

466
00:38:26,960 --> 00:38:28,360
My daughter and I

467
00:38:29,080 --> 00:38:31,120
don't want to be in this town anymore.

468
00:38:32,840 --> 00:38:35,120
Back off.

469
00:38:36,720 --> 00:38:37,840
Back off.

470
00:38:39,280 --> 00:38:40,440
Stay away, all of you.

471
00:38:43,400 --> 00:38:44,600
Don't come closer.

