Back off.

474
00:38:55,000 --> 00:38:56,520
Don't come closer.

475
00:38:56,600 --> 00:38:58,920
Where are you going to live?

476
00:39:00,320 --> 00:39:04,000
There are a lot of bad people outside.

477
00:39:04,640 --> 00:39:06,200
How can you live there?

478
00:39:10,400 --> 00:39:11,400
Back off.

479
00:39:12,280 --> 00:39:13,280
Don't come closer.

480
00:39:17,280 --> 00:39:18,720
Don't come closer.

481
00:39:48,800 --> 00:39:50,480
Your wrongdoing

482
00:39:52,000 --> 00:39:54,280
will be judged by Goddess Som.

483
00:41:28,080 --> 00:41:29,560
Mother.

484
00:42:54,280 --> 00:42:55,720
I bow to you, Goddess Som.

485
00:42:58,400 --> 00:42:59,480
Now,

486
00:43:00,560 --> 00:43:02,080
you both

487
00:43:03,240 --> 00:43:05,480
return to Goddess Som.

488
00:43:06,080 --> 00:43:08,960
May your spirits

489
00:43:09,560 --> 00:43:11,000
rest in peace.

490
00:43:18,960 --> 00:43:22,120
<i>This is the position that offers you</i>

491
00:43:22,200 --> 00:43:24,560
<i>the best chance to have a daughter.</i>

492
00:43:25,160 --> 00:43:26,200
Wow.

493
00:43:26,280 --> 00:43:29,880
<i>Some of you are almost ready to confront</i>

494
00:43:29,960 --> 00:43:32,640
<i>the devils outside.</i>

